# Google SEO Requirements - Every Page Must Comply

## Core SEO Philosophy

**EVERY PAGE** in LaunchBeacon must follow Google's 200+ ranking factors from [Backlinko's comprehensive guide](mdc:https:/backlinko.com/google-ranking-factors). SEO optimization is mandatory, not optional.

