- **Minimum 300 words** per page (longer for competitive keywords)
- **Unique, original content** - no duplicate content
- **Target search intent** - match user's search purpose
- **Include multimedia** - images, videos, interactive elements
- **Regular content updates** - keep information fresh

### 4. Internal Linking Strategy
- **Link to relevant pages** using descriptive anchor text
- **Create content clusters** around topic themes
- **Use breadcrumb navigation** for better site structure
- **Implement related posts/games** sections

